{"tid":545664,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"東京擺低行李去近郊","createTime":"2018-01-30T17:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T18:33:59.000Z","uid":5339,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4e30075f726fed63f7932a539ff1a455808f79","tid":545664,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"嚟梗去東京 會有幾日去箱根河口湖嗰邊<br />\n<br />\nday1上晝擺低行李喺東京 跟住箱根河口湖住3晚<br />\nday4下晝返東京拎返<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過新宿站有得擺行李 不過最多2日 第3日會收走<br />\n想問下大家 東京會唔會有其他地方有得擺行李擺到幾日<br />\n定係拎埋去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1875570be6f538932f1e2dc85f93fdadc430220b","tid":545664,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T21:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔知你幾點落機<br />\n如果下午先去到郊區<br />\n會浪費左第一日<br />\n<br />\n我習慣市區落腳先，行李酒店keep<br />\n第二朝食完早餐輕鬆出發<br />\n叉足電唔使舟車勞頓"},{"pid":"6c7e4925c048a1b434c3819b7a7702949ea5dd0e","tid":545664,"uid":35080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T21:10:03.000Z","msg":"點解唔帶埋去"},{"pid":"6c73f2690c1270f7a211489e40c7a34b3fdc9383","tid":545664,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T21:40:44.000Z","msg":"去幾多日先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce197f07b8cc08bfd03a1355c2ac5da25611db7b","tid":545664,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1875570be6f538932f1e2dc85f93fdadc430220b","tid":545664,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T21:04:59.000Z","msg":"唔知你幾點落機<br />\n如果下午先去到郊區<br />\n會浪費左第一日<br />\n<br />\n我習慣市區落腳先，行李酒店keep<br />\n第二朝食完早餐輕鬆出發<br />\n叉足電唔使舟車勞頓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T23:52:32.000Z","msg":"我day0夜晚到 跟住會喺新宿瞓一晚先 <br />\n我有諗過擺東京嗰邊嘅酒店<br />\n不過我去完近郊返到嚟東京 唔係住返新宿嗰間 <br />\n會去上野嗰邊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564989702dc843cc320bf5c9def71ee517fe2b34","ti